Golden Rule

Ask yourself one question before starting:

«Can ACF comfortably manage the data entry?»

- Yes → Use ACF + Plugin if business logic is needed.
- Yes → Use Only ACF if no business logic is needed.
- No → Build the entire solution as a Custom Plugin.

