Architecture Principle

ACF
│
├── Data Structure
├── Admin UI
├── Content Management
└── Validation

Custom Plugin
│
├── Business Logic
├── Automation
├── Frontend Rendering
├── Integrations
├── APIs
├── Performance
└── Custom Features

Final Principle

«Never build a custom admin interface if ACF already solves the content management problem.

Never force ACF to solve problems that belong to application logic.

Use each tool for what it does best.»